Form Mask

Input masks can be used to force the user to enter data conform a specific format. Unlike validation, the user cant enter any other key than the ones specified by the mask.

(999) 999-9999
dd/mm/yyyy
e.g "999-99-9999
+40 999 999 999
e.g a*-999-a999
$ 999,999,999.99
~9.99 ~9.99 999
e.g "99%"
e.g "999.999.999.9999"
